info.author: Alexander I. Young, Moeen Nehzati
info.name: snipar
info.summary: Library and command line scripts for inferring identity-by-descent (IBD) segments shared between siblings, imputing missing parental genotypes, and for performing family based genome-wide association and polygenic score analyses.
